column4: Meh, I updated to gutsy for one package only, it got a few extra dependancies.  Now I reverted back to Fiesty and I am getting the following error trying to install php5-dev: php5-dev: Depends: libssl-dev but it is not going to be installed
it was not designed to upgrade then downgrade, youll probably have more problems than just that
should I just upgrade for the hell of it?
yea i would, im running gutsy right now just fine
